cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of deep learning techniques, specifically Multi-Resolution Convolutional Neural Networks, for improving ultrasound imaging. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of deep learning for solving an inverse problem involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper also mentions the use of computationally heavy despeckling methods, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
